{
  "stem": "521.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And after a while, when the weather became colder and colder, and my shoe wasn't warm enough, my big toe and the small toe started to freeze over.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It turned black or dark blue.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I said, well, if it's going to go on like this, I'm going to lose my toes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And if I lose my toes I'm going to lose my life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I decided I'm going to report it that I cannot go out to work anymore.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So since it was a combination of concentration camp and forced labor, there was such a thing that I have decided that I'm not going to go out, so I was staying in, and I was staying in all winter.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Now to tell you how life was in-- in that camp, I have to tell you there was a huge big container which one was where the water was kept.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Now the container was as big as I would say as a small room, and it was filled with water.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And this water was serving for washing yourself, washing your dish, and washing-- and drinking of it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So the dish was, of course, dirty, and we didn't wash our hands because we needed the water to drink.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the food which they have given us, it was two times.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Once, in the morning, it was some hot-- they called it a coffee.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I-- I said, as my wife mentioned it to me sometime, it was like black coal instead of coffee.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then in the evening, we got another thing which they called the soup.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
